	(text "LoRa Telemetry RX - RF board (E22 + OLED)\nStacks directly on top of the main board (DevKitC-1+power): J4\n(male header, RX_Connectors sheet) is mounted on this board's\nBACK side in the PCB layout, plugging down into main's female\nsocket - board sits right-side-up, nothing flipped. Config\nbutton + link LED are broken out via jumper wires (J5); OLED\n(J3) is jumper-wired too so the screen stays visible once\nstacked." (at 12.7 70 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5))) (uuid "5293d47b-ccde-477e-abef-414c326fc0ed"))
